</div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wyh1665702766539.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wyh1665702766539.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wyh1665702766539\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      run\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"wyh1665702766539__run_66547\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Set or clear breakpoints on <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">run</span> statements. </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"wyh1665702766539__topic_d19565e1_d19566e1_d19567e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wyh1665702766539__p_d19568e1_d19569e1_d19570e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">RUN</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">on</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">off</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wyh1665702766539__topic_d14112e1_d14113e1_d14114e1_d14115e1_d14116e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d647652e71\">\n                        \n Arguments\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wyh1665702766539__d6568e22\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">on</code>—set breakpoints. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wyh1665702766539__d6568e27\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">off</code>—cancel breakpoints. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wyh1665702766539__topic_d14117e1_d14118e1_d14119e1_d14120e1_d14121e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d647652e90\">\n                        \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wyh1665702766539__p_d19577e1_d19578e1_d19579e1\">When <code class=\"ph codeph\">run</code> breakpoints are set, the debug command line appears before any <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">run</span> ProcScript statement is executed.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"c